# About
Ephp, so easy!!!

# Features
(1) easy & fast
(2) no namespace
(3) Nginx or Apache rewrite the url, not php

# Code rule
(1) variable name use lowercase and underline
(2) model class
1. file name "usermodel.php" class name "usermodel"
2. only model class have CONST

# Env
Linux Nginx & Apache PHP Redis MySQL

# PHP Extension
phpredis & PDO_MYSQL

# Rewrite rule
(1) Nginx http.conf:
if (!-d $request_filename) {
    rewrite ^/([a-z]+)/([a-z]+)/?(.*)$ /index.php?ctrl=$1&act=$2$3 last;
    break;
}

(2) Apache .htaccess:
<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
	RewriteEngine on
	RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d
	RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f
	RewriteRule ^([a-z]+)/([a-z]+)/?(.*)$ index.php?ctrl=$1&act=$2$3& [L]
</IfModule>

# Vist example
localhost/ctrl/act?query_string
	
